page.title: 09CENSUS MATERIAL
page.content: The most popular{names in 1851}are George 5,Ann 4,Mary 3,Elizabeth 3, Henry 3,John 2,William 2.The most popular{second names}are Wilkinson 5, Laking 5,Rotherforth 4,Peat 4,Billam 3,Robinson 2,Simpson 2.The{jobs}that are still done in our days are Butcher Taylor & Grocer, Scholar, House servant, General servant and Farm servant.These are four jobs telling you what they did a Grocer sells fruit and vegetable,The scholar was a school -child. The butcher sells meat and the house servant washes up and tidies up the house.The biggest familis on my sheet are Wilkinson and Laking.These are the jobs that men did.Agricultural Labouring,Scholar,General Servant,Farm Servant,Butcher,Taylor and Grocer.These are women's jobs in 1851- Scholar, General Servant,House Servant.
